      "content": "That sounds good in theory, but I'm worried they'll see right through \"evolving with the community.\" If the reporter asks point-blank, \"Isn't this just a complete reversal because of the donor feedback we got last week?\" what's the specific line we use to ensure they don't report it as a flip-flop? We need to make sure the sentiment scores stay in the green.",
